      <a href="/P2450/contact-me-html" style="color:#0066CC;" class="font-bold">Contact Us</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- Page Hero -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 px-4" style="min-height:40vh;">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src="/P2450/images/home-3.jpg" alt="Mobile dog grooming van" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" fetchpriority="high" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center text-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center" style="min-height:40vh;">
    <span class="inline-block text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">📍 Ryton, Tyne and Wear</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4">Our Services</h1>
    <p class="text-lg" style="opacity:0.9;">Everything your dog needs, done in our mobile grooming van, right outside your door.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Services Introduction -->
<section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4" style="color:#001F3D;">The Pampered Pouches Package</h2>
        <p class="mb-4" style="color:#003D7A;">During every visit your barking buddy will be treated to a bath, clip and nail trim. We take care of everything in our state of the art mobile grooming van, so your house stays spotless and stress-free.</p>
        <p class="mb-6" style="color:#003D7A;">It is quick, convenient and all done within an hour. With one to one attention your dog remains calm and gets the TLC they truly deserve.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
            <span style="color:#001F3D;" class="font-medium">Done within an hour</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
            <span style="color:#001F3D;" class="font-medium">One to one attention throughout</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
            <span style="color:#001F3D;" class="font-medium">No mess in your home</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
            <span style="color:#001F3D;" class="font-medium">Your dog stays calm and relaxed</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden" style="border:2px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <img src="/P2450/images/675389.jpg" alt="Dog after a professional groom" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" width="219" height="292" style="width:100%;height:auto;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Service Cards -->
<section class="py-16 px-4" style="background:#F2F7FC;">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-center mb-12" style="color:#001F3D;">What Every Visit Includes</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden" style="border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="p-6 text-center" style="background:#D9E8F7;">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-2">🛁</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color:#001F3D;">Bath</h3>
          <p style="color:#003D7A;">A thorough, gentle wash using quality shampoo suited to your dog's coat. We rinse and dry your dog completely before moving on to the clip.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden" style="border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="p-6 text-center" style="background:#D9E8F7;">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-2">✂️</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color:#001F3D;">Clip</h3>
          <p style="color:#003D7A;">A professional clip tailored to your dog's breed and coat type. We take care to follow the natural shape of your dog and keep them comfortable throughout.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden" style="border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="p-6 text-center" style="background:#D9E8F7;">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-2">💅</div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color:#001F3D;">Nail Trim</h3>
          <p style="color:#003D7A;">Safe and careful nail trimming to keep your dog comfortable and active. Overgrown nails can cause discomfort, so we always include this as standard.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Pricing Section -->
<section class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-center mb-4" style="color:#001F3D;">Pricing</h2>
    <p class="text-center mb-8" style="color:#003D7A;">Pricing varies depending on your dog's breed, coat type and size. Get in touch and we will give you a personalised quote.</p>
    <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 text-center" style="background:#EBF3FB;border:2px solid #B3D1F0;">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📋</div>
      <p class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color:#001F3D;">Request a Quote</p>
      <p class="mb-6" style="color:#003D7A;">Call us or send a message and we will get back to you with a price tailored to your dog.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="tel:+447946469445" style="background:#0066CC;" class="text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">Call 07946 469445</a>
        <a href="/P2450/contact-me-html" class="px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity" style="border:2px solid #0066CC;color:#0066CC;">Send a Message</a>
