    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl" style="border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="text-3xl flex-shrink-0">⏱️</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color:#001F3D;">Saves You Time</h3>
          <p style="color:#003D7A;">No need to drop off and collect your pet. We come to you at a time that suits your schedule.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl" style="border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="text-3xl flex-shrink-0">🏠</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color:#001F3D;">Your Home Stays Clean</h3>
          <p style="color:#003D7A;">All grooming is done inside our van. No wet dog mess, no clipped fur on your floor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl" style="border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="text-3xl flex-shrink-0">😌</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color:#001F3D;">Less Stress for Your Dog</h3>
          <p style="color:#003D7A;">No other dogs around, no waiting cages. Your dog gets calm, one to one attention from start to finish.</p>
        </div>
