      <div class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl" style="border:1px solid #B3D1F0;">
        <div class="text-3xl flex-shrink-0">📍</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2" style="color:#001F3D;">We Cover Your Area</h3>
          <p style="color:#003D7A;">We operate throughout Newcastle, Gateshead and Durham. Based in Ryton, we are always nearby.</p>
        </div>
